Flickr::API2
============

Perl interface to the Flickr API.

This module is based on Flickr::API by Cal Henderson, forked and updated.

Changes from Version 1:

 * Update API URLs to api.flickr.com
 * Remove XML libraries
 * Return Perl structure
 * Use JSON API at Flickr
 * Update inheritance methods
 * Fix dependencies
 * Use Module::Install instead of ExtUtils::MakeMaker
 * Add unit tests

Still to change:

 * Hand back better data structures
 * Throw exceptions when deserved rather than return half-arsed structs
 * Separate response object from HTTP::Response object.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP::UserAgent
  Digest::MD5
  HTTP::Request
  HTTP::Response
  URI
  Test::More


